2. What are the three main types of memory in the modal model?
3. What is **sensory memory** (include duration)?
4. What is the capacity of **short-term memory**?
5. What is **chunking**? Give an example.
6. Name the three components of **working memory**.
7. What is the difference between **episodic** and **semantic memory**?
8. What is **implicit memory**? Give one example.
9. What is the **priming effect**?
10. What is **long-term potentiation (LTP)**?

